  "title": "Warehouse Administrator (Junior)",
  "description": "<p>Job Summary:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are seeking a reliable and proactive Warehouse Administrator to support daily warehouse operations. This junior role is ideal for someone with a keen eye for detail, a strong sense of responsibility, and a positive, team-oriented attitude. The role offers hands-on experience in a dynamic warehouse environment with opportunities to grow.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Key Responsibilities:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>• Assist in managing inventory records and stock accuracy using warehouse systems</p>\n<p>• Handle documentation for inbound and outbound shipments</p>\n<p>• Coordinate with drivers, suppliers, and internal teams to support smooth operations</p>\n<p>• Maintain organized records of goods received, delivered, and stored</p>\n<p>• Support periodic stock checks and assist during audits</p>\n<p>• Ensure cleanliness and safety standards are upheld in the warehouse</p>\n<p>• Provide general administrative support to the operations Executive and Team</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>• Basic computer literacy (Microsoft Excel, data entry skills preferred)</p>\n<p>• Good communication and teamwork skills</p>\n<p>• Positive attitude and willingness to learn</p>\n<p>• Able to work in a warehouse environment and comfortable with physical tasks when needed</p>",
